title: Little hit, big win; Royals beat Jays for 2-0 lead in ALCS (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,338 Little hit, big win; Royals beat Jays for 2-0 lead in ALCS (Yahoo Sports) The Kansas City Royals kept waiting for Blue Jays ace David Price to give them some hope. It turned out to be Toronto's leaky defense that provided it. After managing one hit over six innings, Ben Zobrist's easy fly that somehow fell for a hit began a five-run rally against Price in the seventh inning Saturday.
